OL,3,C'I'm about to head in and fight':
OL,4,CHannah Spencer sworn in as Green MP
OL,6,FLise McNally spoke to Gorton and
OL,7,FDenton's new MP Hannah Spencer as she
OL,8,Farrived to Parliament.
OL,10,FThe winner of the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,11,Felection Hannah Spencer has been sworn
OL,12,Fin to Parliament as the Green Party's
OL,13,Fnewest MP.
OL,15,FMs Spencer is the first Green MP to
OL,16,Fever come into parliament on a by-
OL,17,Felection win and before she entered
OL,18,Fparliament, she spoke to ITV News
OL,19,Fabout her aims as an MP.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
