OL,3,C'I'm about to head in and fight':
OL,4,CHannah Spencer sworn in as Green MP
OL,6,FShe said: "One of the things I want to
OL,7,Fdo is restore trust in politics and I
OL,8,Fthink we've gone some way to show that
OL,9,Fin the election here.
OL,11,F"I think people really recognise that
OL,12,FI'm hard-working and I'm honest and
OL,13,Fdecent, and that I think will heal a
OL,14,Flot of the divisions that we've
OL,15,Fstarted to see.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
