PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772478696
OL,3,C'I'm about to head in and fight':
OL,4,CHannah Spencer sworn in as Green MP
OL,6,F"But I also want to tackle things like
OL,7,Fthe cost of living, the NHS that is
OL,8,Freally broken but can be fixed, and
OL,9,Fgenerally to improve the lives of
OL,10,Fpeople in Gorton and Denton, which I
OL,11,Fknow is possible we just need someone
OL,12,Fwho is going to fight and I'm about to
OL,13,Fhead in and fight."
OL,15,FShe was accompanied by her party
OL,16,Fcolleagues Ellie Chowns (North
OL,17,FHerefordshire) and former party co-
OL,18,Fleader leader Carla Denyer (Bristol
OL,19,FCentral).
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
