OL,3,C'I'm about to head in and fight':
OL,4,CHannah Spencer sworn in as Green MP
OL,6,FThe new MP, aged 34, was called
OL,7,Fforward by Commons Speaker Sir Lindsay
OL,8,FHoyle at the start of parliamentary
OL,9,Fbusiness on 2 March.
OL,11,FMs Spencer then took the religious
OL,12,Foath, holding a bible, and swore
OL,13,Fallegiance to the King.
OL,15,FShe spoke briefly to Sir Lindsay, who
OL,16,Fcould be heard saying "welcome to
OL,17,FParliament" and referencing her
OL,18,Frepresenting a northern constituency.
OL,26,@xD@WOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
