OL,3,C'I'm about to head in and fight':
OL,4,CHannah Spencer sworn in as Green MP
OL,6,FMs Spencer became the fifth Green
OL,7,FParty MP in the House of Commons last
OL,8,Fweek when she topped the ballot in the
OL,9,FManchester seat.
OL,11,FThe Green Party now has the highest
OL,12,Fnumber of seats it has ever had in the
OL,13,FHouse of Commons.
OL,15,FHannah Spencer said: "Having a Green
OL,16,Fin the room is an incredible force for
OL,17,Fpushing people to be better, pushing
OL,18,Fthe government to do better and
OL,19,Fholding them to account and
OL,20,Fscrutinising their decisions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
