OL,3,C'I'm about to head in and fight':
OL,4,CHannah Spencer sworn in as Green MP
OL,6,F"I know we can only do that by having
OL,7,Fmore Greens, and I am proud to be one
OL,8,Fof them."
OL,10,FThe plumber and plasterer beat Reform
OL,11,FUK into second place, with a majority
OL,12,Fof 4,402.
OL,14,FThe Labour Party, which had previously
OL,15,Fheld the seat at the last general
OL,16,Felection, came third with 9,364 votes.
OL,18,FFormer health minister Andrew Gwynne
OL,19,Fannounced in January he was standing
OL,20,Fdown as an MP.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
